# AI App Builder

**Standalone module for Mobile App Creator - Inspired by Base44, significantly enhanced.**

## Features
- Natural language → Full mobile app scaffolds (React Native + Flutter)
- Multi-platform support
- Feature integration (auth, databases, UI components)
- Iterative refinement
- Local execution, no external dependencies for core
- Exports ready for your Mobile App Creator ecosystem

## Installation
```bash
cd ai_app_builder
pip install -e .
